Package: bayesiansurprise
Title: Bayesian Surprise for De-Biasing Thematic Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Dmitry", "Shkolnik", , "dmitry@shkolnik.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Dmitry Shkolnik [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dmitry Shkolnik <dmitry@shkolnik.io>
Description: Implements Bayesian Surprise methodology for data visualization,
    based on Correll & Heer (2017) "Surprise! Bayesian Weighting for De-Biasing
    Thematic Maps". Provides tools to weight event data relative to
    spatio-temporal models, highlighting unexpected patterns while de-biasing
    against known factors like population density or sampling variation.
    Integrates seamlessly with 'sf' for spatial data and 'ggplot2' for
    visualization. Supports temporal/streaming data analysis.
